## Notes

- The `cullMode = .front` + `scale.z = -1` combo is what makes the image wrap on the
  INSIDE of the sphere and read the right way round. If the panorama looks mirrored,
  flip the sign of `node.scale.x` instead.
- `allowsCameraControl = true` gives drag-to-look for free. Gyroscope (later) replaces
  it with a `CMMotionManager` feeding `cameraNode.orientation`.
- All three panoramas must be the same theater from different spots, or the seat-swap
  illusion breaks.
- Keep styling inside the component/page files per `AGENTS.md`. Don't add Config or
  Helpers until something actually needs them.
